Estelle M. CLARK, Plaintiff in Error, v. Frank C. CLARK, Defendant in Error. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. January 4, 1926.) No. 145. Charles A. Wilson (Prank Harvey Pield, of New York City, of counsel), for plaintiff in error. *872William Huek, Jr., of New York City, for defendant in error.

Before HOUGH, MANTON and HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment 11 F.(2d) 871, affirmed with costs.
